slogan_description: Server luwih rapi, obrolan dadi asik karo TempVoice. Channel suara fleksibel, sekali klik langsung dadi.
featured_description: Ewonan server lan jutaan user Discord milih TempVoice.
introduction_description: Kanal voice kang digawe otomatis pas sampeyan gabung ke Channel Creator, lan bakal dibusak pas ora ana wong ning njero.
setup_description: Nyiapake TempVoice karo perintah '/setup' ning server Discord sampeyan. TempVoice bakal ngebuat channel khusus kanggo ngebuat lan ngatur voice channel!
status_description: TempVoice dibagi dadi sawetara bagian kanggo kinerja luwih optimal. Tiap bagian duwe 5 shard sing nangani sekitar 5.000 server Discord.
server_selection: Pilih salah siji server Discord kanggo ngganti setelan TempVoice utawa ngundang bot TempVoice menyang server liyane.
creators_description: Nentokno kepiye channel voice sementara digawe. Mulo tetepno jeneng standar, akehne batesan channel, ijin-ijin lan liya-liyane.
interface_description: Ngidinkno panganggo kanggo ngatur channel voice sementara deweke.
premium_slogan_description: Bukak kabeh fitur tanpa wates. Bisa dibatalno kapan wae.
premium_description: Dadikno TempVoice pas karo karepmu lan nikmati kbebasan tanpa wates.
premium_feature_explaination_1: Use your own embed profile picture, name, text, color and image
premium_feature_explaination_2: Set up more than 3 creator channels, each with its own settings
premium_feature_explaination_3: Remove the vote requirement from all commands for all users
premium_feature_explaination_4: Log what happens to temporary channels when they get modified
premium_feature_explaination_5: Transfer the subscription to any other server
premium_feature_explaination_6: Get a discount if you need premium for more servers
premium_feature_explaination_7: Separately hosted, custom icon, name, status, about me, ability to show the current playing game as channel name
premium_feature_explaination_8: Save 16% with a yearly billing cycle
premium_upgrade_disclaimer: When you upgrade your Premium subscription, you will immediately be charged the difference in the monthly price you have already paid. You can only upgrade your subscription once a month.
placeholder_description_1: Penanda {PRIVACY} bakal dianyari saben 5 menit nalika privasi kanla diubah.
placeholder_description_2: Jeneng role bakal katon senajan kapisah neng daftar anggota sing onlen.
placeholder_description_3: Nduduhake jeneng role sing paling dhuwur neng daftar anggota sing online sing kapisah.
placeholder_description_4: Penanda bakal diganti karo jeneng anyar kanthi cara nggunakke printah '/voice name'. Bagean saka penanda bisa diganti miturut karepe panganggo.
join_support: Apa sampeyan arep mlebu Discord kami?
excordo_quote: Matur nuwun kanggo minatmu karo TempVoice, bot sing bakal ngubah cara sampeyan nggunakke Discord. Sakdawane taun, aku fokus njangkebi kepinginan lan karepe masyarakat kanggo nggawe server Discord sampeyan dadi papan sing luwih apik!
